<NOTE>
<TITLE> yyrAunD dya oyar+l+D.h in eiTi Deij </TITLE>
<HEAD1> yyrAunD dya oyar+l+D.h in eiTi Deij </HEAD1>
<L>
 anek din Age i.nlyAnDer lanDan shahare thAkten ek bhadralok Ar t,nAr chAkar.  bhadraloker  nAm filiyAs fag, Ar chAkarer 
nAm pAsepAr+tu. bhadralok bhArI ekrokhA, yA karben bale bhAben tA karei chhARen. Ar t,nAr chAkarTio
 temni prabhubhak+ta.  
</L><L>
ekdin filiyAs fag bhAblen, prrithibITA to gol, tAhale ekbAr puro prrithibITAke ekbAr chak+kar diye
 Asi nA kena! takhankAr dine to Ar eroplen ityAdi chhila nA, jAhAj Ar Trenai bharsA, tArAo chalta dhIre susthe. tAo filiyAs 
fag hiseb kSe dekhlen ye mAtra Ashi dinei duniyA safar kare felA yAbe. 
</L>

<L>
lokerA shune bhAbla, fag sAheber mAthAy chhiT Achhe. pAsepAr+tuo maniber parikalpanA shune h,nA! kintu fag sAhaber yeman 
kathA teman kAj. talpitalpA b,nedhe tini raonA haye paRlen.  sange challa shrImAn pAsepAr+tu. 
</L>

<L>
bandare anek jAhAj. tArai ekTAy TikiT keTe chaRe baslen dujane. jAhAj yAbe anek dUr. kichhudin parei ela ek 
chama.tkAr samudra, tAr nAm bhUmadhyasAgar. TalTale nIl jal,  AkAshe miSTi rod. tAr chAridike dike nAnAn
 desh. tAr madhye ekTA hala mishar. pAsepAr+tu  shakha chhila ekTu misharer pirAmiDgulo ghure
 dekhe ney. kintu hAte samay nei bale sei ichchhATA pUraN karA gela nA. 
</L>

<L>
bhUmadhyasAgar yekhAne  sheS, sekhAne jAhAj Dhuke paRla ekTA saru jalapathe. tAr nAm suyej. Ar tAr
 parei--omA samudrer jal to nIl hay, ekhAne eman lAl kena?    pAsepAr+tu eman jinis kaxaNo dekhe ni. Asale jaler madhye 
anek lAl lAl sheolA bhese Achhe, tAi jalTAi puro lAl dekhAchchhe. lAler Arek nAm kinA lohit, tAi loke
 samudraTAr nAmai diyechhe lohit sAgar. 
</L>

<L>
dekhte dekhte lohit sAgarao periye ela jAhAj. ebAr nAmAr pAlA. eDen bandare.  anek din pare pAyer nIche shak+ta mATi peye 
filiyAs fag Ar pAsepAr+tu dujanerai mane bejAy Ananda. tabe hAte samay moTe ekdin. par~din fer jAhAje
 uThe raonA, ebAr gantabya bombe, yAke ekhan AmrA bali mumbai. 
</L>

<L>
Arab sAgarer buk chire chalechhe jAhAj. oi dekhA yAchchhe bhArater upakUl.

</L>

<L>
etadin puro yAtrATAi hayechhe jAhAje. ebAr chaRte habe Trene. tAr byabasthA karte chhuTla dujane.
 er madhye b,nAdhla ek samasyA. pAsepAr+tu to Age kakhano bhArate Aseni, tAi edesher rItinItio tAr
 jAnA nei. se bhul kare juto parei ekTA mandirer bhitare Dhuke gechhe. mandirer purohit~rA tAte
 bejAy khAp+pA, pAsepAr+tuke dhare ei mAre to sei mAre. pAsepAr+tur mejAjTio baRa ThAnDA nay. fale
 ekTA mArAmAri b,nedhe uThte derI hala nA, eba.n pAsepAr+tu yakhan mandir theke lambA lambA pA
 fele piThTAn dila, takhan ekjan purohit mATite chi.tpaTA.n, Ar Arekjan nAker rak+ta muchhchhe. 
</L>

<L>
pAsepAr+tu  mandir theke pAliye bhAbla, yAk bAbA jor b,neche giyechhi, maniber kAchhe ghaTanATA
 chepe yAoyAi bhAlo.  
</L>

<L>
odike fag sAheb TikiTer byabasthA kare felechhen. Tren chalchhe pAhARer gA beye, ghana jangaler madhye diye. se Amale Tren chalta 
s+TIm injine. egota As+te As+te, shab+da karta bikaT, Ar dh,noyA yA chhARta se Ar ki balba! kintu bAirer drrishya eta sundar 
ye, dujanei mugdha haye tAi dekhchhen, Ar bhAbchhen AhA duniyA dekhte nA berole eman sab sundar jinis dekhAi hata nA! 
</L>

<L>
tin din chalAr par Tren haThA.t gela theme. kI byApAr? nA, Trener lAin ekhAnei sheS! fag sAheber mAthAy hAt! e ye ghana 
ban. ekhAn theke beroben kI kare? yAke bale ekebAre ki.nkar+tabyabimURha abasthA! kI karA yAy
yAy  bojhAi yAchchhe nA!  kintu tA bale to Ar hAt
 guTiye base thAkle chale nA! fag
 sAhaber mAthA baRa ThAnDA. sAmne cheye dekhen ekTA hAti charchhe. amni Thik kare fellen oi hAtir piThe chaRei yAben tini. 
pAsepAr+tu h,nA, hAti chAlAno to sahaj kathA nay! manib balen ki!
</L>

<L>
 hAti yArA charAy, tAder bale
 mAhut. dekhte dekhte ekjan mAhutao jogAR haye gela. hAtir piThe  basAr janya ye gadi thAke tAke bale hAodA, baner madhye 
Ar se sab kothAy pAoyA yAbe, tAi dui dike duTo bAk+sa b,nedhe tArai ekTAy fag sAheb Ar anyaTAy pAsepAr+tu chaRe basla. Ar 
mAhutbhAyA basla hAtir ghARer upar. oi dyAkho, hAte a.nkush, oiTe diye hAtir kAn Tene dilei hAti bujhte pAre kon dike chalte 
habe. 
</L>

<L>

hAti chhuTechhe jangal bhe\nge. jh,nAkunir choTe fag Ar pAsepAr+tur abasthA karuN.  
</L>

<L>
eman samaye--
</L>

<L>
baner madhya diye saru path diye mas+ta baRa michhil. ekTA shab~deha niye chalechhe.  kintu oi meyeTi
 ke, yAke aman hAt pA b,nedhe niye
 chalechhe, Ar bechArI 
aman AchhARipichhARi kare k,nAdchhe? 
</L>

<L>
mAhut filiyAs fager kAne kAne balla, oke satI karte niye yAchchhe. oi mrritadehaTA or swAmIr. or swAmI mArA gechhe bale 
okeo swAmIr chitAy puRiye mArA habe. 
</L>

<L>
o mA seki? bale shiure oThen fag. 
</L>

<L>
h,nyA, eke bale satIdAha prathA, balla mAhut. eman 
kare kata anAthA meyer prAN yAy. fag ta.txaNA.t Thik kare fellen ye karei hok ei bar+bar prathAr hAt theke meyeTike b,nAchAte 
habe. 
</L>

<L>
kintu kI kare? fag~rA moTe tin~jan, Ar odike etajan pAhArA dichchhe hatabhAginI meyeTike. rAt
 haye gela. kAl sakAle meyeTike chitAy tolA habe. takhan fager mAthAy ekTA  chama.tkAr 
buddhi ela, tini pAsepAr+tur kAne kAne ki ekTA bale dilen. Ar pAsepAr+tuo rAter andhakAre gA DhAkA
 diye chitAr dike egote lAgla. 
</L>

<L>
bhor hate nA hatei lokjan sabAi meyeTike b,nedhe chitAr dike ela. chitAr upare meyeTir swAmIr mrritadeha shoyAno. 
eman samaye haThA.t--o mA, mrritadehaTA naRe chaRe uThala ye! chokh mele chAila, tArpar uThe d,nARAlo!!!
lokjan to bhay peye bAbAre mA re bale meyeTike fele rekhei ye yedike pArla d\ouR. mrritadeha takhan suYog bujhe meyeTir 
kAchhe giye tAke piThe niye sojA filiyAs fager kAchhe upasthit. Asale se to Ar mrritadeha nay, se hala pAsepAr+tu. rAter 
andhakAre chitAr upar theke Asal mrritadehaTA sariye sei jAygAy  shuye chhila. 
</L>

<L>
lokjan khAnikpare fire ese yakhan Asal mrritadehaTA dekhte pela, takhan tAder yA rAgTA hala! kintu tataxaNe hAtir piThe 
chepe fag Ar pAsepAr+tu meyeTike niye anek dUre p,n\ouchhe gechhen. 
</L>

<L>
meyeTir nAm AudA. bhArI miSTi meye. ebhAbe tAr prAN b,nAchAnor janya fag Ar pAsepAr+tuke ye se katabAr dhanyabAd dila se 
Ar ki balba! 
</L>

<L>
ekdin abasheSe orA kalkAtAy ese p,n\ouchhala. ebAr jAhAj dharte habe chIne yAbAr janya. kintu ekhAne b,nAdhla ek bipatti. 
sei ye bombete pAsepAr+tu ekTA mandire mArAmAri karechhila mane Achhe? sei purohit~rA  pulishe giye nAlish karechhila. pAsepAr+tu 
to tA jan~teo pAreni. Ajke haThA.t kalkAtAr pulish hAtkaRA niye pAsepAr+tuke grep+tAr kare basla. fag Ar ki karen. pulishke 
anek kare bojhAlen ye pAsepAr+tu edesher rItinIti nA jene anyAy kare felechhe. sei kathA shune pulish 
pAsepAr+tuke jele nA pure kichhu 
jarimAnA karei chheRe dila. 
</L>

<L>
kalkAtAr pAsh diye baye chelechhe huglI nadI, tAr dhAre mas+ta bandar. sekhAne jAhAje chepe dekhte dekhte filiyAs fag p,n\ouchhe 
gelen chIn desher h.nka.ne. eikhAne ghaTla ekTA bipad. kIrakam bipad bali shono. 
</L>

<L>
ha.nka.ne ekTA hoTele uThlen fag sAheb, sange AudA. Ar pAsepAr+tu gela jAhAjer TikiT kATte. jAhAj chhARAr kathA par din 
bikele. kintu bandare p,n\ouchhe pAse pAsepAr+tu shone ki, jAhAj nAki sei dinai sandhyey chhARbe! tabe to manibke khabarTA 
ekhanai deoyA darkAr! se Amale to Ar fon chhila nA, tAi  pAsepAr+tu  tARAtARi hoTeler dike pA chAlAlo. kintu natun jAygA 
, tAr pathghAT sab achenA. pAsepAr+tur path gela hAriye. anek rAs+tA ghure sheS~mesh dekhe ki fer bandarei fire esechhe, 
Ar jAhAj chheRe dichchhe. takhan pAsepAr+tu bhAbla ki jAni yadi manib konobhAbe khabar peye jAhAje uThe paRe thAken! eibhebe 
seo jAhAje uThe paRla. uThe dekhla jAhAje fag bA AudA kothAo nei. odike jAhAjao chheRe diyechhe!
 takhan pAsepAr+tur maner abasthA bujhtei pAro! 
</L>

<L>

edike pAsepAr+tur derI dekhe filiyAs fag Ar AudA bejAy chintita. par~din bandare giye dekhen jAhAj gata sandhyAytei chheRe 
gechhe! parer jAhAj chhARte anekdin derI.  AudA to bhay peyei Akul. kintu fag sAheber mAthA khub
 ThAnDA. tini prathamei pulishke jAniye rAkhlen ye pAsepAr+tur kh,noj pele yena t,nAke khabar
 deoyA hay. tArpar ekTA chhoTo n\ouko kine fellen. mas+ta baRa samudra kI kare ekTA chhoTo n\oukoy
 pARi deoyA sambhab! kintu fag sAheb abichal. Ashi dine tini puro prrithibI ghure Asbenai. tAi
 jAhAjer janya derI karA saibe nA, n\oukotei yAben. 
</L>

<L>
kata jhaRjal bhe\nge n\ouko ye sheS parYanta jApAne p,n\ouchhal se shudhu fagai jAnen. Ar jAne
 AudA, se prathame bhaye thar thar   kare k,nApchhila. kintu fager sAhas dekhe tArao As+te As+te sAhas hayechhila. 
</L>

<L>
odike pAsepAr+tu to Agei jApAne p,n\ouchhe gechhila. tAr pakeTe ekTAo paysA nei. se bechArI ki kare. bhAgye, o chhoTobelAy 
khAnikTA jimnAs+Tiks shikhechhila. tAr jore o ekTA
 sAr+kAser khelA dekhAnor kAje peye gela. ekdin ekTA byAlAnser khelA dekhAchchhe, eman samaye dekhe ki--o mA, oi ye dUre 
fag Ar AudA base Achhe. dekhei to o khelATelA fele fag Ar AudAr kAchhe hAjir! takhan oder sakaler ki Ananda ye hala! 
</L>

<L>
jApAn theke yete habe AmerikA. tAr janya jAhAjer abhAb nei. dekhte dekhte orA p,n\ouchhe gela sAn frAnsis~ko  bandare. 
</L>

<L>
AmerikA mas+ta desh. epAr theke opAr yAoyAr janya Trene chAp~te habe.  e Tren kintu bhArater Trener mata jangaler 
madhye diye yAy nA, chAridike dhU dhU prAntar tAr madhye dike sojA chale gechhe Trener lAin.  e anchale DAkAter bhArI upadrab. 
tAi  lAiner pAshe pAshe jAygAy jAygAy  s\oinya motAyen. s\oinyader sheS gh,nATi yekhAne tArpar anekTA juRe DAkAtder rAjatwa. 
seikhAne Tren Dhuktei 
DAkAter
 pAl+lAy paRlen filiyAs fag. 
</L>

<L>
se Amaler Tren chalta dhIre dhIre. tAi chalnta  Trenei  DAkAt~rA  hA re 
re re re re kare ese sadalbale uThe paRla. takhano s\oinyader gh,nATi theke Tren beshI dUre egoy
 ni. Tren theme gelei s\oinyarA p,n\ouchhe yete pAre. kint Tren thAmAbe ke? Tren chAlakkei 
DAkAt~rA prathame 
 dharAshAyI kare dila. bipad dekhe pAsepAr+tu chupichupi 
giye injinTA dila khule. byas Trenao d,nARiye gela. 
pAsepAr+tur ei upasthit  buddhite DAkAt~rA nAjehAl haye pAlAlo baTe, kintu yAbAr samaye pAsepAr+tuke b,nedhe niye gela. 
</L>

<L>
kichhu pare s\oinyerA ele Tren AbAr raonA dila. kintu fag sAheb AudAke niye neme paRlen. t,nAr param~p+riya pAsepAr+tuke DAkAtder 
kabale fele rekhe to Ar tini chale yete pAre nA. kichhu sAhasI s\oinya sange niye filiyAs fag kIkare ye dasyuder hAt theke 
pAsepAr+tuke uddhAr kare Anlen, se ki chhAi Amii jAni ye tomAder balba! Ami khAli jAni sei samayeTA AudA 
u.tkanThAy  thar~thariye 
k,nApchhila, Ar yakhan pAsepAr+tuke niye fag fire elen, takhan Anande tAr duchokh diye jhar~jhar kare jal gaRiye paRechhila. 
</L>

<L>
yA hok, parer diner Trene chepe AbAr sabAi raonA dila. Anander kathA ei ye, erpar Ar kono bipad hay ni. Tren p,n\ouchhala 
niu iyar+ke. sekhAn theke jAhAje chepe ATlAn+Tik mahAsAgar pAr karte habe. tabei filiyAs fag AbAr deshe firte pArben. hAte 
samay baRa nei. baRa baRa jAhAj chhARte ekhanao anek derI. tAi fag sAheb ekTA chhoTo sTimAre
 chAp~len. takhankAr dine sTImAr chalta  kaylA puRiye. ATlAn+Tik  mahAsAgar peronor janya yata kaylA darkAr tataTA neoyAr 
mata jAygAi nei se sTImAre.  kintu fag sAheber tAte bhrUxepai nei. mAjhsAgare yakhan kaylA furolo, takhan sabAi balla kI 
upAy? upAy ekTA fag sAheb Agei bhebe rekhechhilen. seimata hukum dilen, stImAre yata kATher jinis Achhe kaylAr badale seguloke 
poRAo. sTImArer mAlik shune hAy hAy kare uThla.   fag ballen, chintA koro nA, Ami sTImArer dAm
 miTiye deba. natun kare Agun peye dekhte dekhte 
sTImAr fer chhuTe challa. 
</L>

<L>
emani kare sTimAr yakhan fag sAheber desh i.nlyAnDe p,n\ouchhala, takhan sTimArer lohAr kholTuku
 abashiSTa Achhe mAtra! 
tAte fag sAheb bichalita nan. tini bichalita anya kAraNe.  
AudA ye t,nAke chupichupi biye karte cheyechhe! ebAr mahA samArohe fag Ar AudAr biye habe. Ar
 pAsepAr+tu? tAr Ananda dekhe 
ke? oi dekho se keman biyer toRjor karte chhuTechhe!
</L>





